{"tid":2077732,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"社工碩士生認非禮男童等罪囚15個月　官：違反誠信須予以譴責 (20:15)","createTime":"2020-06-24T13:22:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T18:02:12.000Z","uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"d8c20250c17f2779614caf92d624aa27e2718333","tid":2077732,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T13:22:04.000Z","msg":"社工碩士生涉3年前在一間中學任職教牧工作期間，與數名學生到長洲宿營，並與一名當時15歲男童單獨相處時偷拍男童祼照、在牀上非禮他，事隔一年聲稱因男童不理他，恐嚇男童發布其裸照到網上。碩士生早前承認各一項向16歲以下兒童作猥褻侵犯、非禮罪及刑事恐嚇罪，今日（24日）在區域法院被判入獄15個月。<br />\n......<br />\n雖然男童案發時表面上同意被告行為，但法庭不能忽視此乃因男童年紀太小，不懂反應，終判被告入獄15個月。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20200624/s00001/1592993310423/%E7%A4%BE%E5%B7%A5%E7%A2%A9%E5%A3%AB%E7%94%9F%E8%AA%8D%E9%9D%9E%E7%A6%AE%E7%94%B7%E7%AB%A5%E7%AD%89%E7%BD%AA%E5%9B%9A15%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88-%E5%AE%98-%E9%81%95%E5%8F%8D%E8%AA%A0%E4%BF%A1%E9%A0%88%E4%BA%88%E4%BB%A5%E8%AD%B4%E8%B2%AC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200624%2Fs00001%2F1592993310423%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%25A2%25A9%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25AA%258D%25E9%259D%259E%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E7%25AD%2589%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E5%259B%259A15%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%258F%258D%25E8%25AA%25A0%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E9%25A0%2588%25E4%25BA%2588%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E8%25AD%25B4%25E8%25B2%25AC&d=Dkz3eIcuz1ZryPyeMF8ZPgKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=0934bf61\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20200624%2Fs00001%2F1592993310423%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E7%25A2%25A9%25E5%25A3%25AB%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25AA%258D%25E9%259D%259E%25E7%25A6%25AE%25E7%2594%25B7%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E7%25AD%2589%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E5%259B%259A15%25E5%2580%258B%25E6%259C%2588-%25E5%25AE%2598-%25E9%2581%2595%25E5%258F%258D%25E8%25AA%25A